_guide_-_Dr_Richard_Dune_4c111e2c-5cc0-42df-b914-99d23b14d0e3.jpg?v=1724764075 1536w" width="1034" height="1590" alt="Mastering learning and development success: A comprehensive guide - Dr Richard Dune -" title="Mastering learning and development success: A comprehensive guide - Dr Richard Dune -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-dBmyGf kIntMx pf-65_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-66_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by iLixe48 via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-68_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">In the fast-evolving landscape of Learning and Development (L&amp;D), organisations often fall into common traps that hinder the effectiveness of their training initiatives. These pitfalls, while frequently overlooked, can significantly impact the return on investment in L&amp;D and ultimately affect overall business performance.<br>
</p><p class="sc-gFVuLS jpmtwg pf-70_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Here are some common pitfalls in learning and development:
